{"tid":1842113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"本人謹此聲明：今生今世將與大陸人不同桌、不同事、不同行","createTime":"2020-01-25T13:59:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T14:27:57.000Z","uid":146558,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c40f48589b61c5d13a0ba18b2659d74847c50b09","tid":1842113,"uid":146558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:59:41.000Z","msg":"經歷過03嘅大家都明白大陸人嘅禍害有幾深<br />\n話之佢呢一刻即刻支爆，再教育過都要起碼30年至60年，就算佢哋變到同日本人一樣咁有衛生常識都好，我呢世都唔會見到<br />\n<br />\n不同桌：喺餐廳見到大陸人搭枱要即刻離開，至少都要去第二張枱，要將佢哋喺餐廳完全孤立，最好做到佢哋方圓一張枱都冇人<br />\n<br />\n不同事：如果冇可避免要喺同一間公司見到嘅話， 對話距離至少要有3米，非對話時刻必須距離15米，繼續喺工作環境上將佢哋完全孤立<br />\n<br />\n不同行： 喺街見到大陸人要即刻彈開，最好距離15米，至少3米，當佢哋係怪物咁就得，全方位孤立佢哋，保障自己"},{"pid":"95d802a102716d113cd1b407201452894e657400","tid":1842113,"uid":146558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T14:12:39.000Z","msg":"本人謹此聲明：今生今世將與大陸人不同桌、不同事、不同行"},{"pid":"c95a5e841a7181bb20422803461d44ed66b7b717","tid":1842113,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T14:15:34.000Z","msg":"你邊位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61bbd55888d4ed3d20b970c2af71a11f786fa4db","tid":1842113,"uid":146558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c95a5e841a7181bb20422803461d44ed66b7b717","tid":1842113,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T14:15:34.000Z","msg":"你邊位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T14:16:55.000Z","msg":"香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de56988358cc31f4ef768adf8354b1b2552aab29","tid":1842113,"uid":22628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T14:16:55.000Z","msg":"留係香港嘅中國手足呢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30da1304d828a3e66876f5685fd944eb95375dfd","tid":1842113,"uid":61106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T14:17:50.000Z","ms